Class OIDProviderConfigResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wso2.carbon.identity.discovery.OIDProviderConfigResponse

  • public class OIDProviderConfigResponse
extends Object
    OIDProviderConfigResponse contains the patameters to be written as specified in the spec at https://openid.net/specs/openid-connect-discovery-1_0.html Values are corresponding to the entries specified in the DicoveryConstants class
